Takashi, Haru, z cesty!

338
00:17:21,910 --> 00:17:23,450
Co to děláš, ty malej smrade?!

339
00:17:23,620 --> 00:17:24,580
Kašli na to, střílej!

340
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:35,200
Co...

341
00:17:45,800 --> 00:17:48,060
Žádné unáhlené pohyby!

342
00:17:48,220 --> 00:17:51,400
Ubližovat mým kamarádům je fuj!

343
00:17:51,760 --> 00:17:53,940
FUJ!

344
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:55,110
Haruhi!

345
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:56,860
Haruhi, jste v pořádku?

346
00:17:57,940 --> 00:17:59,060
Ah, Tamaník!

347
00:17:59,610 --> 00:18:00,150
He?

348
00:18:00,360 --> 00:18:01,150
Honey!

349
00:18:01,610 --> 00:18:03,060
Haruhi!

350
00:18:04,230 --> 00:18:05,410
Umíral jsem strachy o tebe!

351
00:18:06,480 --> 00:18:07,910
Netuším, co se stalo,

352
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:09,280
